text: William Dunn (July 1877 – unknown) was an English footballer. His regular position was as a forward. Born in Middlesbrough, he played for South Bank and Manchester United. ==External links== *MUFCInfo.com profile Category:1877 births Category:English footballers Category:South Bank F.C. players Category:Manchester United F.C. players Category:Year of death missing Category:Association football forwards
